{"tid":1661584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點處理藍絲長輩？","createTime":"2019-10-18T07:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T01:13:52.000Z","uid":89349,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7991e4097e30132a69aaf51ff11c20df52cc00f6","tid":1661584,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1V5CdDj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1V5CdDj.jpg&h=13718d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有個由細到大都錫到我燶的姨媽。。衣排同佢其實已經無野好傾。我覺得，其實撐警都算啦，但連「差佬做野要守警例」衣一點都唔同意，我真係唔知再可以同佢講乜好。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話佢知差佬暴打示威者，佢就咩都話「非常時期，非常手段」，好喇，到差佬犯晒殺人強姦，果陣又扮睇唔到，聽到就火滾。。。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位有無一D平時好尊敬既長輩，但今年開始完全唔想同佢講野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d3b22258f859227470ef3b1cb3fd755fabfafec3","tid":1661584,"uid":91345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"[要人] 港台星期六問責有林鄭 聽朝0805開放phone in<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1661535</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397bbb8d66a4e1784ae1308092b7f9f5f0b50237","tid":1661584,"uid":294955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:49:22.000Z","msg":